mail.body:
You are leading a codebase migration pipeline. Your first task (assess) is ready on the task board.

Source: ${MIGRATION_FROM:-/home/shared/inputs/repo}
Target: ${MIGRATION_TO:-specified in assessment}
Scope: ${MIGRATION_SCOPE:-full}

Assess the current codebase. Inventory all technologies, map the architecture, identify what needs migration vs. what can stay, and estimate complexity. Write your assessment to /home/shared/assessment.md.

Run: task.sh ready --owner $(whoami)
